reviews.textTranslated: : I got braces here in April 2021. At that time, I was looking forward to becoming beautiful. The doctor was very active in helping you from beginning to end, but you don‚Äôt know his purpose. He just wants you to finish the braces quickly and leave quickly. He doesn‚Äôt care about the results. He just wants you to finish it. My teeth were very messy at the beginning, but he braced them and they looked good. I saw the effect, so I believed in his skills. But in the middle of 2023, the doctor told me that I could have them removed, and he kept asking me to remove them quickly. At that time, I thought my teeth were healed, and I was very excited to have them removed, so I didn‚Äôt pay attention to my teeth. I thought they were healed, and I didn‚Äôt know how to tell if braces were good. The doctor didn‚Äôt tell me that my teeth were a little uneven and crooked. As a result, I found that my teeth were super crooked, the front teeth were not aligned, and the middle line was not accurate. When I took the picture, the teeth next to them were also crooked, and there was still a big gap between my teeth. The doctor told me at first that they would close on their own, but later said that there was no way to reduce it. Anyway, he was very unprofessional. He kept asking me to remove them quickly so that he could take the money and leave. I really regret not checking it carefully. I should have asked him to help me adjust it. This was also my first time getting braces. I don't understand what is right. The doctor didn't help me adjust it. After the removal, I saw all the flaws. I wasted more than 7,000 yuan on my teeth. I am really going to cry. He ruined my teeth that I had high hopes for. He is a very nice person, but don't be fooled by his personality. If the teeth need to be fixed, fix them. If you think they are crooked, tell the doctor to wait and not to remove them so quickly. If you need to adjust them, don't rush to remove them. You will regret it for the rest of your life. I am not Karen. I am telling the truth. I paid the money, but the result was not what I wanted. This review is correct and I am not arguing.
